houghLine - Class in drawEqu
it represents an equation for each line generated from the hough transform this equation depends on an angle(theta) and a perpendicular line (R)
houghLine(double, double) - Constructor for class drawEqu.houghLine
constructor which initiate the theta ( angle between main axis in the image and the perpendicular on a line ) and R ( perpendicular line )
houghTransform - Class in drawEqu
This is the class which forms the hough transform which is a method for detecting lines in an image along with canny's line detection
houghTransform(int, int) - Constructor for class drawEqu.houghTransform
